Asker 
  - queue[] <component>                 Queue, Order of the components
  - blocked <boolean>                   Indicates if the asker is blocked
  - strict                              Enables the execution-strict mode, if true; Components won't be skippable anymore
  - add                                 Add components
  - remove                              Remove components
  - once                                Execute a component


Component
  - message <string>                    The message or question of the component
  - question <boolean>                  Component-type
  - on_response <function/callback>     Optional callback with 3 helpfull parameteres
  - skipped <boolean>                   Indicates if the component is, or will be skipped